# Checkout with all submodules
 git clone --recursive git@github.com:adamtool/adam.git <foldername>
 make checkout_branch_all

Create a file ADAM.properties with the following lines, just adapted to your own paths:

libraryFolder=/home/thewn/petrigames/mercurial/data/impl/lib
aigertools=/home/thewn/tools/mchyper-0.91/aiger/
mcHyper=/home/thewn/tools/mchyper-0.91/mchyper
abcBin=/home/thewn/tools/abc/abc

